race.comment: NO FOOLING (5) resumes with an attractive profile. He won his first two career starts impressively before tackling a strong 3yo handicap at Caulfield and measuring up very well behind the talented Big Swinger. Any further improvement into his second preparation will see him take a power of beating. MISS ALTAIR (8) resumes. She won two in a row to start last campaign including a dominant four-length maiden win here when fresh, beating Taken who went on to do some nice things in town. Don't mind her resuming at 1000m, she's very sharp and can take this out. CODIGO (1) has a huge weight but is a winner in much better company and deserves it. HARALDUS (2) returns from a break. Progressing well including a win in a Mornington jump-out. Monitor the markets.
